parameters: \n<Thief A>"Heh heh... I never thought we'd meet again."

\n<Thief B>"How've you been, Ameria-chan? Whoa there, don't move. If
you don't listen, you're gonna get hurt."
\n<Thief C>"Hahaha! What's up, you seem pretty lively, huh?"
\n<Thief A>"Hey, hey...! What the hell, there are others here?!"

\n<Thief B>"Don't be scared, it's just three women! We'll take care of
all of them--"
\n<Thief B>"Wait, that woman! She's with the knight who escaped!"

\n<Roselitte>"The knight who escaped...? Could it be, the thief who was
an ally of Deorc?"

\n<Thief C>"This is perfect! Hey, don't move a muscle! I won't let you
escape this time!"
